            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " that follow can test the most patient person on the planet, but there is some reasonable expectation that there will be light at the end of the tunnel, for Ben, that expectation went out the door when nine months rolled on with no Mustang back in his possession.",
